title: T.G.British.Bake.Off-S06-Extra.Slice-Masterclasses-w.subs-720p
description:
And here it is - the complete 2015 Season of

The Great British Bake Off (11 Ep)

plus the accompanying

The Great British Bake Off: An Extra Slice (10 Ep)

plus the Season 6

Masterclasses (4 Ep)

in 1280x720 resolution (the best I can get from the BBC),
renamed such that it should sort in chronological order in your filemanager
both in Windows and Linux.

Enjoy - and please keep it seeded !!!

***************************************************

The Great British Bake Off - Season 6

Master bakers Mary Berry & Paul Hollywood and the incomparable presenting duo of
Mel & Sue are back for the sixth series of The Great British Bake Off.

More info: http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b06566cb/episodes/guide
___________________________________________________

The Great British Bake Off: An Extra Slice - Season 2

Jo Brand is joined by three different celebrity Bake Off fans to shine a spotlight
on the good, the bad and the soggy bottomed from the most recent episode.

More info: http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0656q7b/episodes/guide
___________________________________________________

Masterclasses - Season 6

After ten weeks of baking highs and lows, calm descends on the Bake Off tent
as Mary and Paul take up the reins to make the signature, technical and
showstopper challenges that they set the bakers in the first couple of weeks
of the series. Step by step, they take us through the recipes, methods, tricks and
tips to ensure that even the most amateur bakers can get it right at home every time.

More info: http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b039jx00/episodes/guide
